    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Organized travel documentation streamlines the visit planning process and ensures you\'re always prepared for both planned trips and emergency travel situations. Create a digital folder containing copies of important documents like passports, driver\'s licenses, travel insurance information, and research visa requirements if applicable. Additionally, establish a dedicated travel savings fund specifically for visits, emergency flights, or last-minute travel opportunities. Having these preparations in place reduces stress when booking trips and ensures you can quickly act on opportunities to see each other.'
