    helpText: 'Thoughtful planning maximizes the value of precious time together during visits and reduces decision fatigue when you want to focus on enjoying each other\'s company. Create a comprehensive itinerary with 2-3 must-do activities, several flexible options, and backup indoor/outdoor alternatives based on weather or budget changes. Include specific reservations where needed, transportation details, and estimated costs. Having this structure allows you to make the most of limited time together while maintaining flexibility for spontaneous moments and ensuring you both feel fulfilled by the visit experience.'
